---
title: Korean Beef, Eggplant & Baby-Broccoli Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Mayonnaise
description: Eggplant is known in our storybooks as the veggie ruler! Dress it in the finest sweet and soy flavours and roast it in the oven for a depth of
flavour you didn’t know was possible. Served with garlicky rice and stir-fried beef and veggies, this warming dish is sure to be a crowd pleaser.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65c314d575b401e7c0caaa9b-aceca4bc.jpeg
